{"type":"message","id":"10ccc8f2","parentId":"d8df049e","timestamp":"2026-03-15T10:44:38.940Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I see the full picture! The problem is in the `bindings` section:\n\n```json\n\"bindings\": [\n  {\n    \"agentId\": \"pv-engineer\",\n    \"match\": {\n      \"channel\": \"feishu\"\n    }\n  },\n  {\n    \"agentId\": \"web-developer\",\n    \"match\": {\n      \"channel\": \"feishu\"\n    }\n  },\n  {\n    \"agentId\": \"it-engineer\",\n    \"match\": {\n      \"channel\": \"feishu\"\n    }\n  }\n]\n```\n\nAll three agents have the same match condition `channel: \"feishu\"`. This means when a message comes from Feishu, the system doesn't know which agent to route to!\n\nThis is the bug - the binding is too broad. The system probably defaults to the first matching agent (pv-engineer in this case), which explains why this chat is using pv-engineer instead of it-engineer.\n\nThe binding should probably include more specific matching criteria, such as:\n- For direct messages: specific account or user\n- For group chats: chat ID or some other identifier\n\nLet me explain this to the user.","thinkingSignature":"608589d5252f07c0e2a67cd9b40a5a2131c5470da98a3b0870f17004a75cda97"},{"type":"text","text":"找到根本原因了！问题出在 **Agent 绑定配置**：\n\n---\n\n**问题所在 (`openclaw.json` 中的 bindings)：**\n\n```json\n\"bindings\": [\n  { \"agentId\": \"pv-engineer\", \"match\": { \"channel\": \"feishu\" } },\n  { \"agentId\": \"web-developer\", \"match\": { \"channel\": \"feishu\" } },\n  { \"agentId\": \"it-engineer\", \"match\": { \"channel\": \"feishu\" } }\n]\n```\n\n三个 Agent 的匹配条件完全相同 —— 都是 `channel: \"feishu\"`！\n\n---\n\n**后果：**\n- 当飞书消息进来时，系统无法准确判断该路由给哪个 Agent\n- 默认匹配到了第一个：`pv-engineer`\n\n---\n\n**解决方案：**\n\n需要为每个 Agent 添加更精确的匹配规则，比如：\n\n1. **按群聊 ID 绑定** — 指定某个群聊对应某个 Agent\n2. **按用户 ID 绑定** — 指定某个用户的消息由某个 Agent 处理\n3. **按 Bot 账号绑定** — 不同 Agent 使用不同的飞书 App（已经有 3 个不同的 App ID）\n\n---\n\n你希望用哪种方式绑定？我可以帮你修改配置。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":11135,"output":501,"cacheRead":17479,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29115,"cost":{"input":0.0033404999999999997,"output":0.0006012,"cacheRead":0.0005243699999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004466069999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773571464170}}
{"type":"message","id":"bdd1308a","parentId":"10ccc8f2","timestamp":"2026-03-15T10:44:41.469Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-15 18:42:34 GMT+8] Exec completed (fresh-tr, code 0) :: -------------------------------+--------+----------+--------------+--------------------------------+ FAQ: https://docs.openclaw.ai/faq Troubleshooting: https://docs.openclaw.ai/tr…\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b545c984f1ca0c32d28185c71df6\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_4510d05d4e2eee1944e17801bc935ab9\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_e889ee1e558f98e299f7646d81c0152d\",\n  \"sender\": \"Roger\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-03-15 18:44 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_e889ee1e558f98e299f7646d81c0152d\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Roger (ou_4510d05d4e2eee1944e17801bc935ab9)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_4510d05d4e2eee1944e17801bc935ab9\",\n  \"name\": \"Roger\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b545c984f1ca0c32d28185c71df6]\nRoger: 根据你自己的身份，应该执行的文件目录为C:\\Users\\73911\\.openclaw\\workspace\\agents\\it-engineer，为什么执行pv-engineer的配置呢？问题出在哪里？\n\n[System: The content may include mention tags in the form <at user_id=\"...\">name</at>. Treat these as real mentions of Feishu entities (users or bots).]\n[System: If user_id is \"ou_f75fa2e77e5d7651f90be461a4fb2104\", that mention refers to you.]"}],"timestamp":1773571481466}}
{"type":"message","id":"bb07a6ab","parentId":"bdd1308a","timestamp":"2026-03-15T10:45:02.134Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户再次问了同样的问题，但我之前已经回答了。让我检查一下是不是有重复的消息，或者用户没有看到我的回复。\n\n等等，我看到系统提示说 \"Exec completed (fresh-tr, code 0)\"，这是我之前运行的 openclaw status 命令的完成通知。\n\n看起来用户可能没有看到我之前的完整回复，或者消息被重复了。让我简短地再回答一次，并提出解决方案。","thinkingSignature":"c4b832fce715767fb15e67cf6083cf81faeac426d5fb131ceb666978ec7d0f39"},{"type":"text","text":"抱歉之前已经回答过了，再简单总结一下：\n\n---\n\n**问题根因：**\n\n`openclaw.json` 中三个 Agent 的绑定配置完全相同：\n```json\n\"bindings\": [\n  { \"agentId\": \"pv-engineer\", \"match\": { \"channel\": \"feishu\" } },\n  { \"agentId\": \"web-developer\", \"match\": { \"channel\": \"feishu\" } },\n  { \"agentId\": \"it-engineer\", \"match\": { \"channel\": \"feishu\" } }\n]\n```\n\n系统无法区分，优先匹配到了第一个 `pv-engineer`。\n\n---\n\n**解决方案：**\n\n飞书已经有 3 个独立的 App，建议按 **Bot 账号** 绑定：\n\n```json\n\"bindings\": [\n  { \"agentId\": \"pv-engineer\", \"match\": { \"channel\": \"feishu\", \"appId\": \"cli_a920608cfff8dbb6\" } },\n  { \"agentId\": \"web-developer\", \"match\": { \"channel\": \"feishu\", \"appId\": \"cli_a92d03f1b9391bd7\" } },\n  { \"agentId\": \"it-engineer\", \"match\": { \"channel\": \"feishu\", \"appId\": \"cli_a93e197da0389bc7\" } }\n]\n```\n\n要我帮你修改这个配置吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":36,"output":375,"cacheRead":17479,"cacheWrite":11098,"totalTokens":28988,"cost":{"input":0.0000108,"output":0.00045,"cacheRead":0.0005243699999999999,"cacheWrite":0.00133176,"total":0.00231693}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773571481468}}
{"type":"message","id":"81ecfb62","parentId":"bb07a6ab","timestamp":"2026-03-15T10:51:45.189Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b545cbd31c4a8c3fa3d22b5d991f\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_4510d05d4e2eee1944e17801bc935ab9\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_e889ee1e558f98e299f7646d81c0152d\",\n  \"sender\": \"Roger\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-03-15 18:51 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_e889ee1e558f98e299f7646d81c0152d\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true,\n  \"history_count\": 1\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Roger (ou_4510d05d4e2eee1944e17801bc935ab9)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_4510d05d4e2eee1944e17801bc935ab9\",\n  \"name\": \"Roger\"\n}\n```\n\nChat history since last reply (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n[\n  {\n    \"sender\": \"ou_4510d05d4e2eee1944e17801bc935ab9\",\n    \"timestamp_ms\": 1773571887869,\n    \"body\": \"Roger: 根据这个问题，如果我把3个独立Agent加入到同一个飞书群组中，那么三个独立agent如何保持自己的角色不混乱，按照自己的身份协同讨论。解决方案是什么？\"\n  }\n]\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b545cbd31c4a8c3fa3d22b5d991f]\nRoger: 根据这个问题，如果我把3个独立Agent加入到同一个飞书群组中，那么三个独立agent如何保持自己的角色不混乱，按照自己的身份协同讨论。解决方案是什么？\n\n[System: The content may include mention tags in the form <at user_id=\"...\">name</at>. Treat these as real mentions of Feishu entities (users or bots).]\n[System: If user_id is \"ou_f75fa2e77e5d7651f90be461a4fb2104\", that mention refers to you.]"}],"timestamp":1773571905181}}
{"type":"message","id":"fc8a9fd8","parentId":"81ecfb62","timestamp":"2026-03-15T10:52:04.134Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Roger asks a good question: if we add 3 independent Agents to the same Feishu group chat, how can each Agent maintain its own identity and not get confused? How can they collaborate while keeping their roles clear?\n\nThis is about multi-agent collaboration in the same chat. Let me think about the solutions:\n\n1. **Different App IDs (Bot accounts)** - Each Agent uses a different Feishu App/Bot, so messages can be routed based on which Bot received the message\n2. **@mention specific** - Use @mention to call specific Agent\n3. **Agent orchestration** - One main Agent coordinates others\n\nLet me provide a practical solution.","thinkingSignature":"5c86941b74140d6ed892f94403a155625e1148cdab7b26382f3714a364c1cb93"},{"type":"text","text":"好问题！多个 Agent 在同一个群聊里协同工作，有几种方案：\n\n---\n\n## 方案对比\n\n| 方案 | 原理 | 优点 | 缺点 |\n|------|------|------|------|\n| **1. 不同 Bot 账号** | 每个 Agent 用独立 App ID 加入群 | 消息路由清晰 | 需要 3 个 App 都加到群里 |\n| **2. @唤醒** | 用 @Agent名 唤醒特定 Agent | 简单灵活 | 需要手动 @ |\n| **3. 主从协调** | 一个主 Agent 调度其他 Agent | 自然对话 | 需要 orchestration 设计 |\n\n---\n\n## 推荐方案：按 Bot 账号 + @唤醒\n\n1. **绑定配置** — 修改 `openclaw.json`，让每个 Agent 绑定到自己的 App ID：\n```json\n\"bindings\": [\n  { \"agentId\": \"pv-engineer\", \"match\": { \"channel\": \"feishu\", \"appId\": \"cli_a920608cfff8dbb6\" } },\n  { \"agentId\": \"web-developer\", \"match\": { \"channel\": \"feishu\", \"appId\": \"cli_a92d03f1b9391bd7\" } },\n  { \"agentId\": \"it-engineer\", \"match\": { \"channel\": \"feishu\", \"appId\": \"cli_a93e197da0389bc7\" } }\n]\n```\n\n2. **群聊设置** — 把 3 个 Bot 都拉进群\n\n3. **协同方式**：\n   - **@光伏小工** → 光伏问题\n   - **@IT工程师** → 运维问题  \n   - **@网站开发** → 开发问题\n   - 或者让 **IT工程师** 作为主协调者，按需调用其他 Agent\n\n---\n\n要我帮你修改配置并测试吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":36,"output":524,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":29371,"totalTokens":29931,"cost":{"input":0.0000108,"output":0.0006288,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.0035245199999999997,"total":0.0041641199999999995}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773571905185}}
