rovals.md:38:- This file binding is intenti\r\nonally best-effort, not a complete semantic model of every\r\nC:\\Users\\73911\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\tools\\exec.md:89:Per-agent node binding (use the agent li\r\nst index in config):\r\nC:\\Users\\73911\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\tools\\exec.md:96:Control UI: the Nodes tab includes a sma\r\nll ��Exec node binding�� panel for the same settings.\r\nC:\\Users\\73911\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\tools\\index.md:496:  - Discord thread-bound flows depend \r\non `session.threadBindings.*` and `channels.discord.threadBindings.*`.\r\nC:\\Users\\73911\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\tools\\multi-agent-sandbox-tools.md:70:  \"bindings\": [\r\nC:\\Users\\73911\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\tools\\multi-agent-sandbox-tools.md:352:   openclaw agents\r\n list --bindings\r\nC:\\Users\\73911\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\tools\\slash-commands.md:81:- `/session idle <duration|off\r\n>` (manage inactivity auto-unfocus for focused thread bindings)\r\nC:\\Users\\73911\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\tools\\slash-commands.md:82:- `/session max-age <duration|\r\noff>` (manage hard max-age auto-unfocus for focused thread bindings)\r\nC:\\Users\\73911\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\tools\\slash-commands.md:87:- `/unfocus` (Discord: remove \r\nthe current thread binding)\r\nC:\\Users\\73911\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\tools\\slash-commands.md:130:- Discord thread-binding comm\r\nands (`/focus`, `/unfocus`, `/agents`, `/session idle`, `/session max-age`) require effective thread bindings to be ena\r\nbled (`session.threadBindings.enabled` and/or `channels.discord.threadBindings.enabled`).\r\nC:\\Users\\73911\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\tools\\subagents.md:26:Thread binding controls:\r\nC:\\Users\\73911\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\tools\\subagents.md:28:These commands work on channels tha\r\nt support persistent thread bindings. See **Thread supporting channels** below.\r\nC:\\Users\\73911\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\tools\\subagents.md:87:- `thread?` (default `false`; when \r\n`true`, requests channel thread binding for this sub-agent session)\r\nC:\\Users\\73911\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\tools\\subagents.md:98:When thread bindings are enabled fo\r\nr a channel, a sub-agent can stay bound to a thread so follow-up user messages in that thread keep routing to the same \r\nsub-agent session.\r\nC:\\Users\\73911\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\tools\\subagents.md:102:- Discord (currently the only supp\r\norted channel): supports persistent thread-bound subagent sessions (`sessions_spawn` with `thread: true`), manual threa\r\nd controls (`/focus`, `/unfocus`, `/agents`, `/session idle`, `/session max-age`), and adapter keys `channels.discord.t\r\nhreadBindings.enabled`, `channels.discord.threadBindings.idleHours`, `channels.discord.threadBindings.maxAgeHours`, and\r\n `channels.discord.threadBindings.spawnSubagentSessions`.\r\nC:\\Users\\73911\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\tools\\subagents.md:115:- `/unfocus` removes the binding f\r\nor the current bound thread.\r\nC:\\Users\\73911\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\tools\\subagents.md:116:- `/agents` lists active runs and \r\nbinding state (`thread:<id>` or `unbound`).\r\nC:\\Users\\73911\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\tools\\subagents.md:121:- Global default: `session.threadB\r\nindings.enabled`, `session.threadBindings.idleHours`, `session.threadBindings.maxAgeHours`\r\nC:\\Users\\73911\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\zh-CN\\prose.md:95:��       ������ bindings/\r\nC:\\Users\\73911\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\opencl