ers\\73911\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\zh-CN\\cli\\index.md:529:- `--bindings`\r\nC:\\Users\\73911\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\zh-CN\\concepts\\multi-agent.md:66:Ȼ������ `bindings`����\r\n������ɣ���·����վ��Ϣ��\r\nC:\\Users\\73911\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\zh-CN\\concepts\\multi-agent.md:71:openclaw agents list --b\r\nindings\r\nC:\\Users\\73911\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\zh-CN\\concepts\\multi-agent.md:100:  bindings: [\r\nC:\\Users\\73911\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\zh-CN\\concepts\\multi-agent.md:137:- `binding`��ͨ�� `(cha\r\nnnel, accountId, peer)` �Լ���ѡ�� guild/team id ����վ��Ϣ·�ɵ� `agentId`��\r\nC:\\Users\\73911\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\zh-CN\\concepts\\multi-agent.md:165:  bindings: [\r\nC:\\Users\\73911\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\zh-CN\\concepts\\multi-agent.md:227:  bindings: [\r\nC:\\Users\\73911\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\zh-CN\\concepts\\multi-agent.md:261:  bindings: [\r\nC:\\Users\\73911\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\zh-CN\\concepts\\multi-agent.md:305:  bindings: [\r\nC:\\Users\\73911\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\zh-CN\\gateway\\configuration.md:591:- ʹ�� `bindings[].mat\r\nch.accountId` ��ÿ���˺�·�ɵ���ͬ�� agents.defaults��\r\nC:\\Users\\73911\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\zh-CN\\gateway\\configuration.md:735:### ��������·�ɣ�`age\r\nnts.list` + `bindings`��\r\nC:\\Users\\73911\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\zh-CN\\gateway\\configuration.md:767:- `bindings[]`������վ\r\n��Ϣ·�ɵ� `agentId`��\r\nC:\\Users\\73911\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\zh-CN\\gateway\\configuration.md:782:��ÿ��ƥ��㼶�ڣ�`bin\r\ndings` �еĵ�һ��ƥ����Ŀ��ʤ��\r\nC:\\Users\\73911\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\zh-CN\\gateway\\configuration.md:899:  bindings: [\r\nC:\\Users\\73911\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\zh-CN\\gateway\\doctor.md:120:- `routing.bindings` �� ���� `\r\nbindings`\r\nC:\\Users\\73911\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\zh-CN\\gateway\\doctor.md:124:- `bindings[].match.accountID\r\n` �� `bindings[].match.accountId`\r\nC:\\Users\\73911\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\zh-CN\\install\\fly.md:99:# Required: Gateway token (for no\r\nn-loopback binding)\r\nC:\\Users\\73911\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\zh-CN\\install\\fly.md:176:  \"bindings\": [\r\nC:\\Users\\73911\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\zh-CN\\install\\gcp.md:495:   gcloud projects add-iam-polic\r\ny-binding my-openclaw-project \\\r\nC:\\Users\\73911\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\zh-CN\\start\\wizard.md:186:- ���� `bindings` ��·����վ��\r\nϢ���򵼿���ִ�д˲�������\r\nC:\\Users\\73911\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\zh-CN\\start\\wizard.md:319:`openclaw agents add` д�� `age\r\nnts.list[]` �Ϳ�ѡ�� `bindings`��\r\nC:\\Users\\73911\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\zh-CN\\tools\\multi-agent-sandbox-tools.md:76:  \"bindings\":\r\n [\r\nC:\\Users\\73911\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\zh-CN\\tools\\multi-agent-sandbox-tools.md:357:   openclaw \r\nagents list --bindings","cwd":"C:\\Users\\73911\\.openclaw\\workspace\\agents\\pv-engineer"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773572293922}}
{"type":"message","id":"70d22ab9","parentId":"27b31202","timestamp":"2026-03-15T10:58:27.497Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"找到了！根据文档，bindings 使用的字段是 `accountId`，不是 `appId`。让我读取 feishu.md 的绑定配置示例来确认。","thinkingSignature":"0c995ba39de77f4f0112e2484d779ec8362b499b3c8867c14c6abfa5d266c714"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_tqknuygmbx1v_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\73911\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\channels\\feishu.md","limit":100,"offset":530}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":32045,"output":104,"cacheRead":17479,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49628,"cost":{"input":0.009613499999999999,"output":0.0001248,"cacheRead":0.0005243699999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.010262669999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773572293933}}
{"type":"message","id":"d15edb82","parentId":"70d22ab9","timestamp":"2026-03-15T10:58:27.512Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_tqknuygmbx1v_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\nSet `streaming: false` to wait for the full reply before sending.\n\n### Multi-agent routing\n\nUse `bindings` to route Feishu DMs or groups to different agents.\n\n```json5\n{\n  agents: {\n    list: [\n      { id: \"main\" },\n      {\n        id: \"clawd-fan\",\n        workspace: \"/home/user/clawd-fan\",\n        agentDir: \"/home/user/.openclaw/agents/clawd-fan/agent\",\n      },\n      {\n        id: \"clawd-xi\",\n        workspace: \"/home/user/clawd-xi\",\n        agentDir: \"/home/user/.openclaw/agents/clawd-xi/agent\",\n      },\n    ],\n  },\n  bindings: [\n    {\n      agentId: \"main\",\n      match: {\n        channel: \"feishu\",\n        peer: { kind: \"direct\", id: \"ou_xxx\" },\n      },\n    },\n    {\n      agentId: \"clawd-fan\",\n      match: {\n        channel: \"feishu\",\n        peer: { kind: \"direct\", id: \"ou_yyy\" },\n      },\n    },\n    {\n      agentId: \"clawd-xi\",\n      match: {\n        channel: \"feishu\",\n        peer: { kind: \"group\", id: \"oc_zzz\" },\n      },\n    },\n  ],\n}\n```\n\nRouting fields:\n\n- `match.channel`: `\"feishu\"`\n- `match.peer.kind`: `\"direct\"` or `\"group\"`\n- `match.peer.id`: user Open ID (`ou_xxx`) or group ID (`oc_xxx`)\n\nSee [Get group/user IDs](#get-groupuser-ids) for lookup tips.\n\n---\n\n## Configuration reference\n\nFull configuration: [Gateway configuration](/gateway/configuration)\n\nKey options:\n\n| Setting                                           | Description                             | Default          |\n| ------------------------------------------------- | --------------------------------------- | ---------------- |\n| `channels.feishu.enabled`                         | Enable/disable channel                  | `true`           |\n| `channels.feishu.domain`                          | API domain (`feishu` or `lark`)         | `feishu`         |\n| `channels.feishu.connectionMode`                  | Event transport mode                    | `websocket`      |\n| `channels.feishu.defaultAccount`                  | Default account ID for outbound routing | `default`        |\n| `channels.feishu.verificationToken`               | Required for webhook mode               | -                |\n| `channels.feishu.webhookPath`                     | Webhook route path                      | `/feishu/events` |\n| `channels.feishu.webhookHost`                     | Webhook bind host                       | `127.0.0.1`      |\n| `channels.feishu.webhookPort`                     | Webhook bind port                       | `3000`           |\n| `channels.feishu.accounts.<id>.appId`             | App ID                                  | -                |\n| `channels.feishu.accounts.<id>.appSecret`         | App Secret                              | -                |\n| `channels.feishu.accounts.<id>.domain`            | Per-account API domain override         | `feishu`         |\n| `channels.feishu.dmPolicy`                        | DM policy                               | `pairing`        |\n| `channels.feishu.allowFrom`                       | DM allowlist (open_id list)             | -                |\n| `channels.feishu.groupPolicy`                     | Group policy                            | `open`           |\n| `channels.feishu.groupAllowFrom`                  | Group allowlist                         | -                |\n| `channels.feishu.groups.<chat_id>.requireMention` | Require @mention                        | `true`           |\n| `channels.feishu.groups.<chat_id>.enabled`        | Enable group                            | `true`           |\n| `channels.feishu.textChunkLimit`                  | Message chunk size                      | `2000`           |\n| `channels.feishu.mediaMaxMb`                      | Media size limit                        | `30`             |\n| `channels.feishu.streaming`                       | Enable streaming card output            | `true`           |\n| `channels.feishu.blockStreaming`                  | Enable block streaming                  | `true`           |\n\n---\n\n## dmPolicy reference\n\n| Value         | Behavior                                                        |\n| ------------- | --------------------------------------------------------------- |\n| `\"pairing\"`   | **Default.** Unknown users get a pairing code; must be approved |\n| `\"allowlist\"` | Only users in `allowFrom` can chat                              |\n| `\"open\"`      | Allow all users (requires `\"*\"` in allowFrom)                   |\n| `\"disabled\"`  | Disable DMs                                                     |\n\n[23 more lines in file. Use offset=630 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773572307505}}
{"type":"message","id":"26f8ca79","parentId":"d15edb82","timestamp":"2026-03-15T10:58:37.987Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我看到了正确的格式！\n\n根据文档，bindings 配置应该是：\n- `match.channel`: \"feishu\"\n- `match.peer.kind`: \"direct\" 或 \"group\"\n- `match.peer.id`: 用户 Open ID (ou_xxx) 或群组 ID (oc_xxx)\n\n但这是针对 peer (用户/群聊) 的绑定。对于按账号区分，需要使用 `accountId`。\n\n让我再看看文档中关于 accountId 的说明。","thinkingSignature":"84be3d22b39ada6e4ec36450e34e7314aa617fc0fb816cf5940d0110405107bd"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ssyo10sc2obs_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\73911\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\concepts\\multi-agent.md","limit":100,"offset":130}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":33158,"output":166,"cacheRead":17479,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":50803,"cost":{"input":0.0099474,"output":0.0001992,"cacheRead":0.0005243699999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01067097}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773572307511}}
{"type":"message","id":"76df8d82","parentId":"26f8ca79","timestamp":"2026-03-15T10:58:38.006Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ssyo10sc2obs_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"This lets **multiple people** share one Gateway server while keeping their AI “brains” and data isolated.\n\n## One WhatsApp number, multiple people (DM split)\n\nYou can route **different WhatsApp DMs** to different agents while staying on **one WhatsApp account**. Match on sender E.164 (like `+15551234567`) with `peer.kind: \"direct\"`. Replies still come from the same WhatsApp number (no per‑agent sender identity).\n\nImportant detail: direct chats collapse to the agent’s **main session key**, so true isolation requires **one agent per person**.\n\nExample:\n\n```json5\n{\n  agents: {\n    list: [\n      { id: \"alex\", workspace: \"~/.openclaw/workspace-alex\" },\n      { id: \"mia\", workspace: \"~/.openclaw/workspace-mia\" },\n    ],\n  },\n  bindings: [\n    {\n      agentId: \"alex\",\n      match: { channel: \"whatsapp\", peer: { kind: \"direct\", id: \"+15551230001\" } },\n    },\n    {\n      agentId: \"mia\",\n      match: { channel: \"whatsapp\", peer: { kind: \"direct\", id: \"+15551230002\" } },\n    },\n  ],\n  channels: {\n    whatsapp: {\n      dmPolicy: \"allowlist\",\n      allowFrom: [\"+15551230001\", \"+15551230002\"],\n    },\n  },\n}\n```\n\nNotes:\n\n- DM access control is **global per WhatsApp account** (pairing/allowlist), not per agent.\n- For shared groups, bind the group to one agent or use [Broadcast groups](/channels/broadcast-groups).\n\n## Routing rules (how messages pick an agent)\n\nBindings are **deterministic** and **most-specific wins**:\n\n1. `peer` match (exact DM/group/channel id)\n2. `parentPeer` match (thread inheritance)\n3. `guildId + roles` (Discord role routing)\n4. `guildId` (Discord)\n5. `teamId` (Slack)\n6. `accountId` match for a channel\n7. channel-level match (`accountId: \"*\"`)\n8. fallback to default agent (`agents.list[].default`, else first list entry, default: `main`)\n\nIf multiple bindings match in the same tier, the first one in config order wins.\nIf a binding sets multiple match fields (for example `peer` + `guildId`), all specified fields are required (`AND` semantics).\n\nImportant account-scope detail:\n\n- A binding that omits `accountId` matches the default account only.\n- Use `accountId: \"*\"` for a channel-wide fallback across all accounts.\n- If you later add the same binding for the same agent with an explicit account id, OpenClaw upgrades the existing channel-only binding to account-scoped instead of duplicating it.\n\n## Multiple accounts / phone numbers\n\nChannels that support **multiple accounts** (e.g. WhatsApp) use `accountId` to identify\neach login. Each `accountId` can be routed to a different agent, so one server can host\nmultiple phone numbers without mixing sessions.\n\nIf you want a channel-wide default account when `accountId` is omitted, set\n`channels.<channel>.defaultAccount` (optional). When unset, OpenClaw falls back\nto `default` if present, otherwise the first configured account id (sorted).\n\nCommon channels supporting this pattern include:\n\n- `whatsapp`, `telegram`, `discord`, `slack`, `signal`, `imessage`\n- `irc`, `line`, `googlechat`, `mattermost`, `matrix`, `nextcloud-talk`\n- `bluebubbles`, `zalo`, `zalouser`, `nostr`, `feishu`\n\n## Concepts\n\n- `agentId`: one “brain” (workspace, per-agent auth, per-agent session store).\n- `accountId`: one channel account instance (e.g. WhatsApp account `\"personal\"` vs `\"biz\"`).\n- `binding`: routes inbound messages to an `agentId` by `(channel, accountId, peer)` and optionally guild/team ids.\n- Direct chats collapse to `agent:<agentId>:<mainKey>` (per-agent “main”; `session.mainKey`).\n\n## Platform examples\n\n### Discord bots per agent\n\nEach Discord bot account maps to a unique `accountId`. Bind each account to an agent and keep allowlists per bot.\n\n```json5\n{\n  agents: {\n    list: [\n      { id: \"main\", workspace: \"~/.openclaw/workspace-main\" },\n      { id: \"coding\", workspace: \"~/.openclaw/workspace-coding\" },\n    ],\n\n[324 more lines in file. Use offset=230 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773572317997}}
{"type":"message","id":"6450a570","parentId":"76df8d82","timestamp":"2026-03-15T10:58:45.990Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我明白了！根据文档：\n\n1. 飞书 (feishu) 支持多个账号 (accounts)\n2. 可以使用 `accountId` 来绑定不同的 Agent 到不同的账号\n\n看一下配置中飞书的账号定义：\n- pv-engineer: appId = cli_a920608cfff8dbb6\n- web-developer: appId = cli_a92d03f1b9391bd7\n- it-engineer: appId = cli_a93e197da0389bc7\n\n所以正确的绑定方式应该是使用 `match.accountId`，对应配置中的账号 ID（即 pv-engineer, web-developer, it-engineer）。\n\n让我确认一下格式是否正确。","thinkingSignature":"955fda8138b313dcf933b12c4d721f3bdc1e3248c881ce783965d1e145997706"},{"type":"text","text":"查到了！根据官方文档，正确的字段是 `accountId`（不是 `appId`）。\n\n**正确的绑定格式：**\n\n```json\n\"bindings\": [\n  { \n    \"agentId\": \"pv-engineer\", \n    \"match\": { \"channel\": \"feishu\", \"accountId\": \"pv-engineer\" } \n  },\n  { \n    \"agentId\": \"web-developer\", \n    \"match\": { \"channel\": \"feishu\", \"accountId\": \"web-developer\" } \n  },\n  { \n    \"agentId\": \"it-engineer\", \n    \"match\": { \"channel\": \"feishu\", \"accountId\": \"it-engineer\" } \n  }\n]\n```\n\n其中 `accountId` 对应 `channels.feishu.accounts` 中的账号 ID（pv-engineer, web-developer, it-engineer）。\n\n---\n\n这样配置后：\n- 当消息从 **pv-engineer** 这个 Bot 账号发出时 → 路由给 pv-engineer Agent\n- 当消息从 **web-developer** 这个 Bot 账号发出时 → 路由给 web-developer Agent  \n- 当消息从 **it-engineer** 这个 Bot 账号发出时 → 路由给 it-engineer Agent\n\n要我帮你修改 `openclaw.json` 吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":34330,"output":421,"cacheRead":17479,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52230,"cost":{"input":0.010298999999999999,"output":0.0005052,"cacheRead":0.0005243699999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01132857}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773572318004}}
