{"type":"message","id":"c896cb89","parentId":"b2f567ea","timestamp":"2026-03-15T11:10:34.043Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看起来有多个Agent在群里了！现在Roger在@不同的Agent。让我看看：\n\n1. @H-IT工程师 - ou_40c0cdd2d3b1daf5de376fea1fe191ef\n2. @H-网站开发工程师 - ou_3578e01b431e05c2c52a31dc6be20510\n3. 最新的消息是@我(光伏小工) - ou_52eb44f0e98a08e6bff4c8dbef835a11\n\n看来配置已经生效，不同的Bot被加入到群聊里了。让我介绍自己。","thinkingSignature":"13ba1a45e040fb37b27dfb589fe99104f476bfa1081302f94d965511ba7f63ab"},{"type":"text","text":"大家好！我是 **H-光伏系统开发工程师** 🌞⚡\n\n专注于光伏系统的新建、技改和运维相关技术工作，包括：\n\n- 📐 系统方案设计与造价预算\n- 📊 发电量仿真分析\n- 🔧 设备选型（组件、逆变器、支架）\n- 💡 投资回报分析\n- 🔌 并网技术咨询\n\n有什么光伏相关的问题，随时问我！😊"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":36,"output":226,"cacheRead":9177,"cacheWrite":44671,"totalTokens":54110,"cost":{"input":0.0000108,"output":0.0002712,"cacheRead":0.00027530999999999996,"cacheWrite":0.00536052,"total":0.00591783}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773573023128}}
