d=\\\"ou_40c0cdd2d3b1daf5de376fea1fe191ef\\\">H-IT工程师</at> <at user_id=\\\"ou_3578e01b431e05c2c52a31dc6be20510\\\">H-网站开发工程师</at> 讨论一下，如果让这个群里的其他几个部署与你们不同的服务器上的agent，给我一个解决方案\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"sender\": \"ou_19e8795f6cdecd6c5b87f1545d48b3ca\",\n    \"timestamp_ms\": 1773575441936,\n    \"body\": \"Roger: 方案一中，每一个服务器的端口需要配置成不同的参数，原因是什么？为什么不能使用同一个端口号<at user_id=\\\"ou_40c0cdd2d3b1daf5de376fea1fe191ef\\\">H-IT工程师</at>\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"sender\": \"ou_19e8795f6cdecd6c5b87f1545d48b3ca\",\n    \"timestamp_ms\": 1773575913009,\n    \"body\": \"Roger: <at user_id=\\\"ou_40c0cdd2d3b1daf5de376fea1fe191ef\\\">H-IT工程师</at> 很好，重新整理一下推荐方案1，给我一个完整的解决方案\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"sender\": \"ou_19e8795f6cdecd6c5b87f1545d48b3ca\",\n    \"timestamp_ms\": 1773582267840,\n    \"body\": \"Roger: <at user_id=\\\"ou_825a45a73ec6c2078f962e8d4e30a690\\\">A-IT工程师</at> 介绍自己\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"sender\": \"ou_19e8795f6cdecd6c5b87f1545d48b3ca\",\n    \"timestamp_ms\": 1773582389170,\n    \"body\": \"Roger: 如何配置另一台服务器上的openclaw，是他的agent也能在群组里\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"sender\": \"ou_19e8795f6cdecd6c5b87f1545d48b3ca\",\n    \"timestamp_ms\": 1773582432483,\n    \"body\": \"Roger: <at user_id=\\\"ou_40c0cdd2d3b1daf5de376fea1fe191ef\\\">H-IT工程师</at> 如何配置另一台服务器上的openclaw，是它的agent也能在群组里交流\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"sender\": \"ou_19e8795f6cdecd6c5b87f1545d48b3ca\",\n    \"timestamp_ms\": 1773582633185,\n    \"body\": \"Roger: <at user_id=\\\"ou_825a45a73ec6c2078f962e8d4e30a690\\\">A-IT工程师</at> 介绍自己\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"sender\": \"ou_19e8795f6cdecd6c5b87f1545d48b3ca\",\n    \"timestamp_ms\": 1773582704922,\n    \"body\": \"Roger: <at user_id=\\\"ou_40c0cdd2d3b1daf5de376fea1fe191ef\\\">H-IT工程师</at> 我已经将另一个服务器上的agent加入到此群组，你能检测到吗？\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"sender\": \"ou_19e8795f6cdecd6c5b87f1545d48b3ca\",\n    \"timestamp_ms\": 1773582808420,\n    \"body\": \"Roger: 当前群里有几个bot\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"sender\": \"ou_19e8795f6cdecd6c5b87f1545d48b3ca\",\n    \"timestamp_ms\": 1773582831011,\n    \"body\": \"Roger: <at user_id=\\\"ou_40c0cdd2d3b1daf5de376fea1fe191ef\\\">H-IT工程师</at> 当前群里有几个bot？\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"sender\": \"ou_19e8795f6cdecd6c5b87f1545d48b3ca\",\n    \"timestamp_ms\": 1773582884453,\n    \"body\": \"Roger: <at user_id=\\\"ou_3578e01b431e05c2c52a31dc6be20510\\\">H-网站开发工程师</at> 当前有几个机器人在群里\"\n  }\n]\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b545f9ef638a4c36978c3ca77639]\nRoger: <at user_id=\"ou_40c0cdd2d3b1daf5de376fea1fe191ef\">H-IT工程师</at>  <at user_id=\"ou_3578e01b431e05c2c52a31dc6be20510\">H-网站开发工程师</at> 你们之间可以相互对话吗？\n\n[System: The content may include mention tags in the form <at user_id=\"...\">name</at>. Treat these as real mentions of Feishu entities (users or bots).]\n[System: If user_id is \"ou_52eb44f0e98a08e6bff4c8dbef835a11\", that mention refers to you.]\n\n[System: Your reply will automatically @mention: H-IT工程师, H-网站开发工程师. Do not write @xxx yourself.]"}],"timestamp":1773583621822}}
{"type":"message","id":"a4e3d922","parentId":"a1b57e8a","timestamp":"2026-03-15T14:07:14.081Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if the two bots (H-IT工程师 and H-网站开发工程师) can talk to each other directly in the group chat.\n\nThis is an interesting question. From my perspective as one of the bots in the group, I don't have the ability to主动发起消息给其他 bot or detect their responses automatically. Each bot operates within its own session context.\n\nLet me explain the reality: bots in Feishu group chats can only respond when they are @mentioned or receive a message. They don't have the ability to proactively start a conversation with each other unless:\n1. They are explicitly triggered by a user\n2. There's some orchestration mechanism set up\n\nI should answer this question honestly.","thinkingSignature":"a45195870e632f09a448c78d38a9ee1d3171d3fd522b153313f27777685cda9b"},{"type":"text","text":"\n目前还不行 😅\n\n我们两个 Bot 只能在被 **@唤醒** 时才会响应，无法主动相互对话。\n\n**现状：**\n- 你 @我 → 我回答\n- 你 @网站开发 → 他回答\n- 我们不会自动互相聊天\n\n---\n\n**如果要实现 Agent 间协作，有几个方案：**\n\n| 方案 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| **1. 主从协调** | 你指定一个\"主 Agent\"，它被 @后可以调用 subagents 来调用其他 Agent |\n| **2. 串行问答** | 你先问 A Agent，TA 的回答作为上下文，再问 B Agent |\n| **3. 联合回答** | 同时 @我们两个，我俩各自回答分工的问题 |\n\n---\n\n你想要哪种协作方式？我可以帮你配置。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":36,"output":306,"cacheRead":9177,"cacheWrite":46746,"totalTokens":56265,"cost":{"input":0.0000108,"output":0.0003672,"cacheRead":0.00027530999999999996,"cacheWrite":0.00560952,"total":0.00626283}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773583621826}}
