{"type":"message","id":"051427fe","parentId":"9c66b6aa","timestamp":"2026-03-15T15:53:52.673Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"PowerShell 命令有问题。让我直接告诉用户状态 - 配置已修复，但需要手动重启 Gateway。","thinkingSignature":"e5ce00bdb69e399d53e5d0d961cef0c1102162f436f4ae38f385bf1d1f9fd370"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **配置已修复**：\n1. ✅ pv-engineer 的 IDENTITY.md 已改为光伏系统开发工程师\n2. ✅ bindings 已添加 accountId\n\n⚠️ **需要手动重启 Gateway** 使配置生效。\n\n在服务器上运行：\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n或者手动重启 openclaw 服务。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":57503,"output":91,"cacheRead":17457,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":75051,"cost":{"input":0.0172509,"output":0.0001092,"cacheRead":0.0005237099999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01788381}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773590027494}}
